ntische Ästhetik trifft.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh1 aArnold, Antje, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBreuer, Ingo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBusch, Anna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCastelli, Anna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDelhey, Yvonne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEsselborn, Hans, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFleig, Anne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGribnitz, Barbara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHerrmann, Leonhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJaglarz, Monika, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aJastal, Katarzyna, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aJaśtal, Katarzyna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKiermeier, Ursula, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKita-Huber, Jadwiga, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKording, Inka, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKłańska, Maria, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMüller, Nadja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMüller-Salget, Klaus, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRoussel, Martin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchlinzig, Marie Isabel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSocha, Caroline, econtributor.4ctb4ht